            <a href="#"><img src="../images/paw.png" alt="paw.png" />Let's Start <img src="../images/Separator.png" alt="Separator.png" /></a>
            <span>1/6 Steps Complete!</span>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

<div class="row no-gutters set-plan-bg">
    <div class="col-md reg-content align-items-center text-center users-can-do">
        <div class="row m-2 p-2">
            <div class="col-md">
                <button class="back-button" @onclick="OnGoBack">Back</button>
                <button class="next-profile-bottom" @onclick="OnGoNext">Next</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md">
                <div class="form-floating">
                    <span class="title">How Do I Meet Success?</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row no-gutters align-items-center justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-8 col-sm-10 pe-3">
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <img src="../images/group-profile.png" class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 float-sm-start fixed-size" alt="group-profile.png" />
                    <p class="col-md-10 col-sm-12 text-start"><strong>Create a profile that provides all the details.</strong> Who are you and what can you do for your buyers? When are you available for work and contact?</p>
                    <hr/>
                </div>
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <img src="../images/idea-startup-svgrepo-com.png" class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 float-sm-start fixed-size" alt="idea-startup-svgrepo-com.png" />
                    <p class="col-md-10 col-sm-12 text-start"><strong>Don’t be afraid to post your experience.</strong> How did you start your business? What clients have you served so far?  What are your goals for consumers?</p>
                    <hr/>
                </div>
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <img src="../images/group-people.png" class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 float-sm-start fixed-size" alt="group-people.png" />
                    <p class="col-md-10 col-sm-12 text-start"><strong>To keep our pet-loving community safe, we may have to verify your profile.</strong> You can legitimize your business more by providing us a business ID that is insivisble to buyers.</p>
                    <hr/>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-8 col-sm-10 ps-3">
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <img src="../images/infographic-svgrepo-com.png" class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 float-sm-start fixed-size" alt="infographic-svgrepo-com.png" />
                    <p class="col-md-10 col-sm-12 text-start"><strong>Don’t provide inaccurate or misleading information.</strong> Consumers will apperciate an upfront approach to your products, services, and vendor profile. </p>
                    <hr/>
                </div>
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <img src="../images/ecommerce-svgrepo-com.png" class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 float-sm-start fixed-size" alt="ecommerce-svgrepo-com.png" />
                    <p class="col-md-10 col-sm-12 text-start"><strong>You can stand out from other vendors by showcasing your unique branding.</strong> We offer plans to display your logo & virtual store! <a href="">Learn More about our options here.</a></p>
                    <hr/>
                </div>
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <img src="../images/group-solicit.png" class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 float-sm-start fixed-size" alt="group-solicit.png" />
                    <p class="col-md-10 col-sm-12 text-start"><strong>Don’t solicit irrelevant products, services, and contents in PetZONE 360™.</strong> This includes things that are not pet, pet parent, or animal related. </p>
                    <hr/>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex m-2 p-2 justify-content-center">
            <div class="d-inline-flex">
                <input id="agree" type="checkbox" class="form-check" /><label class="p-2">I Agree with PetZONE360™ Terms of Service</label>
            </div>
            <div class="d-inline-flex">
                <input id="agree" type="checkbox" class="form-check" /><label class="p-2">I Agree with PetZONE360™ Privacy Policy</label>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row m-2 p-2">
            <div class="col-md">
                <button class="next-profile-bottom" @onclick="OnGoNext">Next</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
@code
{
    
    public void OnGoNext()
    {
        _navigationManager.NavigateTo($"/vendor/setplan", true);
    }

    public void OnGoBack()
    {
        _navigationManager.NavigateTo($"/vendor/intro", true);
    }
}
